    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Devices, often having a basic shape similar to a boat-shaped weaver's shuttle, but used to carry thread as a spool; used for sewing, knotting, tatting, and embroidery. May be highly decorative and of precious materials.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
